name: Ocean Dive (Bbomb11)
description:
An Oceanic Diving Game. Dive through the deep seas to find sunken tresaure!

Made for Ludum Dare 48.

The WebGL builds weren't working so I found a way to make it work, which was to use a development build. I would recommend downloading it, but the webGL build works, you just have to wait a bit for it to load. Oh Well.

Made With Love.
